snippet.title: Amber Guyger's Frantic 911 Call, Is Losing Your Job Worse Than Murder? Let's Talk About It
snippet.description:

The 911 call and future consequences for Dallas police officer Amber Guyger. This is the result of shooting unarmed Botham Jean in his apartment in Dallas Texas after she entered thinking it was her own.
